commit.message:
re PR target/69444 (recent changes broke x64_64 -> powerpc crosscompiler build)

	PR target/69444
	* config/rs6000/sfp-machine.h: Fix a typo in #ifndef - __NO_FPRS__
	instead of ___NO_FPRS__.

From-SVN: r232805
